front.title: •Short-range Fighters
front.gametext: Once per game, target one non-unique starfigihter on table. Draw destiny. If destiny < X, retrieve X Force, where X = number of copies of that card you have on table. (Immune to Sense.) OR Take one non-unique starfighter into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.
front.lore: Imperial batlestations keep squadrons of TIE/Ins on constant patrol.
